text: Nevado Pastoruri is a mountain in central Peru located in the center of Pachapaqui, in the Aquia District, in the Bolognesi Province in the Ancash Region. It is located in the Cordillera Blanca, a mountainous chain that forms part of the Cordillera Occidental of the Peruvian Andes.El Nevado Pastoruri ==References== Category:Mountains of Ancash Region Category:Mountains of Peru
title: Nevado Pastoruri
